import React from 'react'
import {Col, Row} from 'antd'
import {SearchCardWrapper} from '../atoms'
import {Avatar} from '../../../../UIComponents/Avatar'
import {Text} from '../../../../UIComponents/Typography/Text'

export const SearchCard = ({size, title, text, src}) => {
    return (
        <SearchCardWrapper>
            <Row gutter={[12, 0]} align='middle'>
                <Col>
                    <Avatar
                        size={size}
                        shape='square'
                        imgUrl={src}
                    />
                </Col>
                <Col flex={1}>
                    <Row>
                        <Col span={24}>
                            <Text>{title}</Text>
                        </Col>
                        <Col span={24}>
                            <Text color='var(--grey-dwed)'>
                                {text}
                            </Text>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </SearchCardWrapper>
    )
}
